11#include "video/rtp_video_stream_receiver_frame_transformer_delegate.h"
12
13#include <utility>
14#include <vector>
15
16#include "absl/memory/memory.h"
17#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtp_descriptor_authentication.h"
18#include "rtc_base/task_utils/to_queued_task.h"
19#include "rtc_base/thread.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22
23namespace {
24class TransformableVideoReceiverFrame
25 : public TransformableVideoFrameInterface {
26 public:
27 TransformableVideoReceiverFrame(std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject> frame,
28 uint32_t ssrc)
29 : frame_(std::move(frame)),
30 metadata_(frame_->GetRtpVideoHeader()),
31 ssrc_(ssrc) {}
32 ~TransformableVideoReceiverFrame() override = default;
33
34 // Implements TransformableVideoFrameInterface.
35 rtc::ArrayView<const uint8_t> GetData() const override {
36 return *frame_->GetEncodedData();
37 }
38
39 void SetData(rtc::ArrayView<const uint8_t> data) override {
40 frame_->SetEncodedData(
41 EncodedImageBuffer::Create(data.data(), data.size()));
42 }
43
44 uint32_t GetTimestamp() const override { return frame_->Timestamp(); }
45 uint32_t GetSsrc() const override { return ssrc_; }
46
47 bool IsKeyFrame() const override {
48 return frame_->FrameType() == VideoFrameType::kVideoFrameKey;
49 }
50
51 std::vector<uint8_t> GetAdditionalData() const override {
52 return RtpDescriptorAuthentication(frame_->GetRtpVideoHeader());
53 }
54
55 const VideoFrameMetadata& GetMetadata() const override { return metadata_; }
56
57 std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject> ExtractFrame() && {
58 return std::move(frame_);
59 }
60
61 private:
62 std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject> frame_;
63 const VideoFrameMetadata metadata_;
64 const uint32_t ssrc_;
65};
66} // namespace
67
68RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::
69 RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate(
70 RtpVideoFrameReceiver* receiver,
71 rtc::scoped_refptr<FrameTransformerInterface> frame_transformer,
72 rtc::Thread* network_thread,
73 uint32_t ssrc)
74 : receiver_(receiver),
75 frame_transformer_(std::move(frame_transformer)),
76 network_thread_(network_thread),
77 ssrc_(ssrc) {}
78
79void RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::Init() {
80 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&network_sequence_checker_);
81 frame_transformer_->RegisterTransformedFrameSinkCallback(
82 rtc::scoped_refptr<TransformedFrameCallback>(this), ssrc_);
83}
84
85void RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::Reset() {
86 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&network_sequence_checker_);
87 frame_transformer_->UnregisterTransformedFrameSinkCallback(ssrc_);
88 frame_transformer_ = nullptr;
89 receiver_ = nullptr;
90}
91
92void RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::TransformFrame(
93 std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject> frame) {
94 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&network_sequence_checker_);
95 frame_transformer_->Transform(
96 std::make_unique<TransformableVideoReceiverFrame>(std::move(frame),
97 ssrc_));
98}
99
100void RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::OnTransformedFrame(
101 std::unique_ptr<TransformableFrameInterface> frame) {
102 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate> delegate =
103 this;
104 network_thread_->PostTask(ToQueuedTask(
105 [delegate = std::move(delegate), frame = std::move(frame)]() mutable {
106 delegate->ManageFrame(std::move(frame));
107 }));
108}
109
110void RtpVideoStreamReceiverFrameTransformerDelegate::ManageFrame(
111 std::unique_ptr<TransformableFrameInterface> frame) {
112 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&network_sequence_checker_);
113 if (!receiver_)
114 return;
115 auto transformed_frame = absl::WrapUnique(
116 static_cast<TransformableVideoReceiverFrame*>(frame.release()));
117 receiver_->ManageFrame(std::move(*transformed_frame).ExtractFrame());
118}

120} // namespace webrtc
